Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.85,0:00:13.52,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}The brilliant glow of this sky, does it carry right into your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.83,0:00:22.91,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,1600)\3c&H141414&}The melody you heard in your dream, it plays like the silence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.53,0:00:28.12,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Even if your hands are still far from that dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.12,0:00:33.34,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Come now and remember that kindly voice
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.34,0:00:46.28,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(50,200)\3c&H141414&}Someone was there singing for you, the happiness they sang about
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:55.68,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Sound of the sky, echo on high, break through that overwhelming sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.68,0:01:00.62,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Everything that shines in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.62,0:01:06.08,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,400)\3c&H141414&}Is part of the real world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.34,0:01:15.55,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,200)\3c&H141414&}Even your tears can't leave you here to stay forever
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.71,0:01:27.51,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,4000)\3c&H141414&}In this gentle light pouring down onto you, play tomorrow's song
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:29.14,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&00&}Kanata's Day Off - Hair Ties
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.40,0:22:46.47,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - put these feelings together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.47,0:22:49.26,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}And sing of how important they are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.61,0:23:07.74,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I was so happy that I cried
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.58,0:23:13.71,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}It hurt so bad that I laughed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.54,0:23:22.55,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}But that all just goes to show that I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.55,0:23:26.68,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,800)}Let's just walk it slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.68,0:23:28.37,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}Everybody singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.37,0:23:32.66,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Just tell me a bit of what you think
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.66,0:23:33.98,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}You're just my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.98,0:23:39.99,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - even though they might waver
Dialogue: 1,0:23:37.02,0:23:39.99,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&\an8}I know, you know, little happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.99,0:23:45.82,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I want us to echo on forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.73,0:23:45.82,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&\an8}Can you hear my precious note?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.82,0:23:52.20,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}All these words that there are can't even describe it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.20,0:23:57.95,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1400)}Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.95,0:24:02.59,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1400)}Can you hear it? Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.26,0:01:49.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.95,0:01:58.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:11.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's the way we'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:12.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.73,0:02:14.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,As for where we condu-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.73,0:02:17.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading out, Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:21.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.52,0:02:24.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Already planning to use your first paycheck?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:25.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:27.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sending some home,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:31.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and I thought I'd send some souvenirs back, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:32.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A little treat for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:34.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:39.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The first month was just training so you didn't get anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.16,0:02:40.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Excited, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:42.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. But I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:49.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that we were usually paid late, and then in military scrip.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:51.06,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are. Good work this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.16,0:02:55.94,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:01.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think I would get real money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:05.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you do. Why do you think we have our other busine-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:12.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, um... Er... There's a flea market in town today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.09,0:03:13.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your first time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.60,0:03:16.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Your first paycheck and your first day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.18,0:03:19.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A first time for everything and right on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.02,0:03:22.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about your day job and take a good look at everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:23.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:33.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going then!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:44.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to say anything suspicious around Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.83,0:03:45.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But just think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:52.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting paid in the middle of nowhere and without even a late supply shipment?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:04:01.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And... she actually believed you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:04.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She accepts what she gets. That's Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:05.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:10.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike you two. You found out where we got the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:12.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And how.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:18.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:22.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we forget about our day jobs, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:31.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got character.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:32.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.74,0:04:35.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's just one fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:37.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The price isn't going any lower.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:45.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I didn't notice you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.30,0:04:59.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.47,0:05:02.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We haven't run into any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:05.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've run into some.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.87,0:05:09.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got an idea to take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:10.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You in?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.84,0:05:13.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me more about this idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.47,0:05:20.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This one is nice too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.55,0:05:42.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the fine shopkeeper. You selling these?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:52.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you like our goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:53.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.21,0:05:59.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But, there's just one fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.43,0:06:01.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.81,0:06:06.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got this many. It would take some work and a few connections to sell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:10.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And we don't have the resources for that, you get what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:11.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:14.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a no-discount policy here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.25,0:06:16.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The price is part of the taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.79,0:06:20.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't ask you to lower the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.33,0:06:25.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just take them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.08,0:06:25.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.39,0:06:34.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and shoot. If you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.01,0:06:35.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause before you can,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:40.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,this gun in my hand would blow your head clean off, just like your hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:42.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.14,0:06:46.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not very smart, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.90,0:06:54.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what you get for taking me lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.77,0:06:57.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:30.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I warned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.96,0:07:36.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Punk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:39.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You one of their friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:45.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:54.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The car!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:56.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:07:59.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.00,0:08:00.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But the souvenirs for the Don?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:02.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Worthless if we're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.99,0:08:04.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.13,0:08:06.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No one said anything about maniacs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:10.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're never coming back again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:16.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.02,0:08:17.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.65,0:08:21.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You can get up now, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:25.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I was scared for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.76,0:08:28.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But it looks like we fooled them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:31.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.81,0:08:37.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. If the mob got a foothold here, our business would go kaput.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:41.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little give-and-take.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:42.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.99,0:08:46.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You will be giving us our fee for this little play.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:50.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my. Mikhail, you do have a sense of humor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:53.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:55.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:58.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we talk business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.12,0:09:01.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't I take those?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:05.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you bust their car there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.11,0:09:09.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.05,0:09:10.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.44,0:09:12.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:15.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It looked like someone busted their car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:21.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And there were some goods that they bought at the flea market.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:25.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't I say I bought those and we split the profits?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:31.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems we've reached an agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:32.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.07,0:09:37.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So the play's finally over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.71,0:09:40.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was quite a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.25,0:09:41.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What was?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:45.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You were completely in character, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:50.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone discovered that we're distilling this, we'd have more than a court-martial on our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:54.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct violations of the anti-trust laws and tax laws.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.00,0:09:56.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,At worst, charges of treason.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:10:00.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. We picked up this business after the ones before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:03.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And Rio's never been against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.27,0:10:05.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a bit surprised too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:15.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was surprised myself at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:18.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This calvados was my mother's favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.57,0:10:22.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And it was made here at the fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:30.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe your mother was responsible for your station here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:38.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an3\pos(1840,1050)}Sound of the Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:43.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an1\pos(80,1050)}Sound of the Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.01,0:10:51.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going then!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:11:00.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister Yumina!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.83,0:11:03.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:06.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's wonderful, Seiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.59,0:11:15.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:18.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is their first visit to the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.29,0:11:21.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The priest will be there today. So, just for today...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:22.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.21,0:11:29.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't start causing her problems now. At least let her do your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.65,0:11:31.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I won't let her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:35.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not? You always tell me to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:37.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.55,0:11:44.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that, Mishio.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:48.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.96,0:11:56.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,¥10.25.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:01.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Look where you're going, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:04.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I didn't notice you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:09.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, these bumpkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.63,0:12:09.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:13.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems they've heard about our business.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.64,0:12:18.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:19.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:24.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But Miss Naomi, tell me, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.52,0:12:29.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've had enough money in my purse to buy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.03,0:12:31.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If I ask for it, I could just buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:37.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What if someone came in and wanted to buy that dolphin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.91,0:12:41.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did someone say they wanted to buy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:43.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No, just a hypothetical question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.75,0:12:48.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... I would...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.82,0:12:53.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I would tell them that dolphins were really scary people-eating animals and make sure they didn't buy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:57.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You're a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.85,0:13:00.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and that dolphin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.15,0:13:04.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep it until you say you don't want it anymore, so relax and worry all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:10.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll buy everyone's souvenirs first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:16.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... Dad, Mom, Grandpa, Grandma,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.17,0:13:21.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma and Grandpa Warren, Great-grandma,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:23.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and Grandma Nanae next door!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:28.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.63,0:13:30.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There's so much stuff to choose!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:31.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:34.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.64,0:13:38.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mishio?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.37,0:13:41.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you out shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:43.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like she's looking for a box.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:45.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A box?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.68,0:13:48.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this. Did you see one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:52.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:58.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I help you look for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:00.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here, Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.96,0:14:04.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to buy souvenirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:08.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking for something wonderful to send to my family back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:09.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not in a hurry-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:10.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.26,0:14:24.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why Mishio said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:30.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.61,0:14:33.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's quite nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.41,0:14:35.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This one is nice too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:40.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister Yumina?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.45,0:14:43.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Miss Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.53,0:14:45.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Mishio?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:50.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A box?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.21,0:14:52.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. She said it was important.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:55.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.36,0:15:02.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When her mother died, all of her family's belonging's were taken from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.18,0:15:08.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's supposed to be a memento that her mother left her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:12.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Whenever there's a flea market, she always goes to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:18.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I said something wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:21.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I received my first paycheck yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:24.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And I told her I was sending presents back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.91,0:15:27.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.65,0:15:29.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.50,0:15:32.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We are trying to be her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.86,0:15:37.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If she were still jealous of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.50,0:15:41.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,then it's because I'm not good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:59.24,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama, which is more important to you, me or your treasure box?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.24,0:16:01.31,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.14,0:16:07.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.21,0:16:16.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:26.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:36.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,These are Treize's famous firecrackers! They'll crack like thunder! How about 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:45.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister... Sister Yumina...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:46.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:48.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.50,0:16:56.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The car!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:05.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'm not Yumina.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:14.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister! Sister Yumina!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:18.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.\NKeep up the good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.61,0:17:22.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.97,0:17:24.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:29.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.79,0:17:35.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that car... yours, Miss Naomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.66,0:17:37.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you two did that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.94,0:17:43.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry! There's ¥150 in here, so
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.09,0:17:44.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.69,0:17:48.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:52.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You can keep that. I already got my payment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.44,0:17:59.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Naomi! That box!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.23,0:18:07.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,These ideographs mean "beautiful rice stalk".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:14.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Carve them into her seal and I assure you she will have a life as full of happiness as a bountiful field of rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:16.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.75,0:18:20.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Miho, aren't you so happy to receive such a great fortune?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.97,0:18:28.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find Mishio?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:35.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I had done everything to be her family,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.75,0:18:38.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm still not good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:42.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you are trying hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:48.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:55.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful! You found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.78,0:18:57.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Take good care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:19:00.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an irreplaceable memento from your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:02.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:04.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This box...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:07.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.71,0:19:20.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio was taken in by the church after she lost her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:26.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Her father was sent to the front lines and never returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:28.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And her mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:34.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio's family lived in the Eastern region of Binnenland.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:35.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.69,0:19:39.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the town stricken by the Invisible Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:47.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When they arrived here in Seize, her mother was already showing symptoms, and soon after...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:52.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:56.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She said, "Sorry I can't do your hair anymore."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:20:04.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And she told me... to have the person who cares about me most tie my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.31,0:20:08.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you tie it, Yumina?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.36,0:20:16.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Man lives on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.57,0:20:22.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after being separated from those we love and suffer as though dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:27.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We still live on. We can live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:32.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That strength is our sorrow. Our love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:38.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:39.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.76,0:20:41.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:55.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's already in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:57.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'll go soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:03.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You had a long day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.16,0:21:07.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I didn't really want to wash my hair,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:09.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but things happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.58,0:21:14.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Oh! Oh! Let me dry your hair for you, Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.58,0:21:17.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.13,0:21:24.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So you didn't buy the dolphin?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.13,0:21:27.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that would be your little treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.77,0:21:33.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio, do you believe in destiny?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:35.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.11,0:21:41.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, something that felt like it happened today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.15,0:21:44.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That was enough of a treat for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.82,0:21:53.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe in it. I don't like the idea that anything's already decided for you before you even get a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.79,0:21:57.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I do believe
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.00,0:22:01.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,that one small thing someone does
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:03.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,can work its way up and up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.67,0:22:07.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and change someone's life in an amazing way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.35,0:22:14.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's destiny,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.14,0:22:18.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,then maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.02,0:22:19.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.95,0:22:27.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,D-flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.00,0:22:37.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Rio had a wonderful day today, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.55,0:24:14.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(960,405)\c&H020202&\bord0}Next time: Chirping Crickets - Floating Lights on the River
